SUMMARY:Repair PDX: RPDX Repair Café @ Leaven Common House
DESCRIPTION:Category: Social Activities\nCost: FREE\nNote: All Repair Cafés
  and most workshops are free. Bring broken items to be repaired by volunte
 ers.\nFormat: In-person\nInfo: Volunteers fix small appliances\, bikes\, c
 lothing. Tool/knife sharpening and Kintsugi repair available. Registration
  form recommended.\nWebsite: https://www.repairpdx.org\nDetails: Operating
  since 2013. Part of global Repair Café movement promoting sustainability 
 and community connection. Great for learning basic repair skills. Contact 
 503-893-9656 or repairpdx@gmail.com.
LOCATION:Leaven Common House\, 5431 NE 20th Ave\, Portland\, OR 97211
URL:https://www.repairpdx.org
